    {
      "id": "doc-001",
      "name": "QA Process",
      "order": 0,
      "content": "<h1><b>Welcome</b></h1><b>Welcome to the buildee team! </b>This guide will help you get started and provide essential resources to begin working effectively as part of the QA team.<div><div class=\"doc-cards\">\n        <div class=\"doc-card\">\n          <strong class=\"doc-card__title\">Production</strong>\n          <span class=\"doc-card__body\"><a href=\"https://app.buildee.com\">app.buildee.com</a></span><span class=\"doc-card__body\">Live user-facing environment.</span>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"doc-card doc-card--tinted\" style=\"--card-tint: #225d09;\">\n          <strong class=\"doc-card__title\">QA</strong>\n          <span class=\"doc-card__body\"><a href=\"https://htpps://qa.buildee.com\">qa.buildee.com</a><font color=\"#1e293b\" face=\"ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, monospace\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.5px; background-color: rgb(238, 243, 239);\"><br></span></font>Auto-deployed when code merges into the <code>develop</code> branch</span>\n        </div>\n        \n        <div class=\"doc-card\"><strong class=\"doc-card__title\">Staging</strong><span class=\"doc-card__body\"><a href=\"https://staging.buildee.com\">staging.buildee.com</a><br>Pre-production validation<br>Shares DB/users with prod <br>Most stable, hosts automation runs</span></div><div class=\"doc-card\">\n          <strong class=\"doc-card__title\"><span style=\"font-family: Inter, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, sans-serif;\">Default test env</span></strong><strong class=\"doc-card__title\"><font color=\"#64748b\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px;\">QA</span></font></strong>\n        </div></div><h1>Tools Overview</h1><div><div class=\"doc-cards\">\n        \n        <div class=\"doc-card\">\n          <strong class=\"doc-card__title\">JIRA</strong>\n          <span class=\"doc-card__body\">https://simuwatt.atlassian.net/</span>\n        </div>\n        \n        <div class=\"doc-card\">\n          <strong class=\"doc-card__title\">Slack</strong>\n          <span class=\"doc-card__body\">Team communication &amp; CI notifications</span>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"doc-card\">\n          <strong class=\"doc-card__title\">Postman</strong>\n          <span class=\"doc-card__body\">API testing</span>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"doc-card\">\n          <strong class=\"doc-card__title\">Playwright</strong>\n          <span class=\"doc-card__body\">E2E browser automation framework</span>\n        </div></div><h1>QA Workflow in Jira</h1><p><span style=\"font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: -0.26px; font-family: Inter, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, sans-serif;\">QA validates all tickets in <code><span style=\"color: rgb(29, 205, 123);\"><b><span style=\"color: rgb(20, 173, 102);\">\"Ready for QA\" </span></b></span></code>status.&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: -0.26px;\">Once testing has passed, the ticket should be moved to ✅ Accepted by QA. If testing fails, move it to ❌ Rejected by QA.</span></p><h1>QA Validation Requirements</h1><div>Before closing a ticket, add validation results in the comments:</div><div><br></div><div><ul><li>Scope of testing — What was tested and in which environment</li><li>Results — Pass/Fail for each scenario</li><li>Notes / Edge cases — Any noteworthy details, including edge cases covered</li></ul></div><p><span style=\"font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: -0.26px; font-family: Inter, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, sans-serif;\"><br></span></p></div></div>",
      "createdAt": "2026-04-22T21:43:09.690Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-04-23T01:43:20.536Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "doc-002",
      "name": "Important Links",
      "order": 1,
      "content": "<p></p><h1><b>Testing Materials</b></h1><ol><li><b>Survey List &amp; Utility Programs</b>:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://survey.buildee.com/survey/97f1c75b-f820-4819-aab6-72455bdbec20\">https://survey.buildee.com/survey/97f1c75b-f820-4819-aab6-72455bdbec20</a></li><li><b>Manual OCR Testing:</b>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1KcOg3PxdZPf9I22e33XC-mSB1K4j8OcUO5zf249EiH0/edit?tab=t.0#heading=h.o3tx3tkn6xf6\">https://docs.google.com/document/</a></li><li><b>Calculation Examples:</b> <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1EwLRBahizQ3zwXGpyNckO8HZrOJDo4WWgj0j-RQ7hRg/edit?gid=1744492772#gid=1744492772\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/</a></li></ol><h1>ESPM-Related Documentation</h1><div><ol><li><b>ESPM Production</b>: <a href=\"https://portfoliomanager.energystar.gov/pm/login\">portfoliomanager.energystar.gov/pm/login</a></li><li><span style=\"font-family: Inter, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, sans-serif;\"><b>ESPM API Docs</b>: <a href=\"https://portfoliomanager.energystar.gov/webservices/home/test/api/meter\">API test </a>· <a href=\"https://portfoliomanager.energystar.gov/pdf/reference/Testing_Web_Services_en_US.pdf\">PDF reference</a></span></li><li><b>ESPM Score Workflow</b>: <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1xml2X_4VMSRFNw5_vTsrj8C4rtl01IB8WfhyIm0Cnqo/edit?tab=t.0#heading=h.qh47dvlcpe83\">Google Doc</a></li><li><b>Measure ESPM Impact Scores</b>: <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1-iScQ9P42ES6za8zch2mk731Ky12_ZNWpiK2mL42lTo/edit?tab=t.0#heading=h.n5dbkfpnr2wr\">Google Doc</a></li><li><b>Property Types Eligible for 1–100 ENERGY STAR Score</b>: <a href=\"https://www.energystar.gov/buildings/benchmark/understand-metrics/property-types/eligible-score\">energystar.gov</a></li></ol></div><div><br></div><p></p>",
      "createdAt": "2026-04-22T21:45:12.527Z",
